ets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀其實屆屆世盃都有31隊要登機嫁啦，但人地出線隊點柒都柒唔撚過小組包尾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n包尾廢柴真係有樣睇，咁簡單既道理都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eb557006fdb431a64368a3faecd1a78a7c5766","tid":719841,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4457e678d350716e205f6377b1bf0822bd549cd","tid":719841,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"No Germany"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}